name: Heart Banner Tattoo - customizable
description:
Give your loved ones a classic tattoo this holiday - the red heart on wood is delicate and simple and looks great on the wall. 

This one is customizable with a name or word. You can also request one with a longer banner for a phrase. Customizations add just one day to transit time.

name: Custom Tattoo Plaque - Any color, any shape, any design. Mostly.
description: You've always wanted a tattoo, but you're not ready for the commitment. Or you've never wanted a tattoo, but you love the art of classic flash. Maybe you are in search of a great gift - what's better than a bright, personalized tattoo you can hang anywhere? Don't have any ideas? No worries, I have oodles - from hearts with banners proclaiming your love to tattoos memorializing your moped, I'll help you get the right tattoo plaque. Commissions have been my specialty for years, and I've developed a quick system that helps us all be excited about the end product. When you purchase a plaque: Click on "Contact" to the right and describe your tattoo plaque dreams to me and include the best way to get in touch with you. You will receive a draft of the image within 7 days. For the holiday season, you'll receive a draft within 2 business days. Custom plaques typically take 1 week to complete. If you are aching for a tattoo plaque more quickly than that, click "Contact" and let me know. You can still order to receive in time for Christmas when you use rush shipping!

name: Gypsy Skull Tattoo - white and black on a scalloped plaque
description: This gypsy skull tattoo lives on a black field over a pine plaque with decorative edges. She's painted in white waterproof india ink, and is the perfect way to start your tattoo collection - without the pain or permanence. She is about 11 inches by 9 inches, and is a nicely sized but intimate piece with delicate linework. Given that she's a skull, she's just a touch macabre, but not so much that she gives anyone the creeps. Read the blog post to learn how she was made.

name: A Wise Owl Tattoo - white on natural on a squared plaque
description:
Owls and wise banners: two staples of classic tattoos. "Wisdom Outweighs Wealth" seems like just what a friendly owl would tell you during a hard time, or just to puff up your ego a bit.

This owl is about 11 inches by 10 inches and is painted in india ink on a pine plaque.
